  <ButtonText>k__BackingField: On doit maintenir notre allure, je compte sur vous
    deux pour maintenir le moteur
  <NpcText>k__BackingField:
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d57cec67bb2a1a945ada3b66d3cb9bf5, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3973df86522e4b743879172e3518e737, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Mais c\u2019est irresponsable !"
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 44ec2a6625f7a934dab5754819bfeb2e, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 368af27e801a8f643a3763179d93db07, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - On va tous mourir !
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d57cec67bb2a1a945ada3b66d3cb9bf5, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3973df86522e4b743879172e3518e737, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - Tais toi la poiscaille !
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d57cec67bb2a1a945ada3b66d3cb9bf5, type: 2}
